Check the 5sf blog for more thoughts! http://5secondfilms.com/5sfblog/5sf-behind-the-scenes-on-set-with-andrew-w-k/

On a pleasant day in New York this December, party commander / rocker / all around nice guy Andrew W.K. agreed to meet with a couple of us to shoot a 5-second film. Having never seen the site before, he easily jumped into the concept and afterwards was more than happy to humor me as I geeked out in front of him.
